==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Snub-nosed
<hw>Snub"-nosed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having a short,
flat nose, slightly turned up; <as>as, the <ex>snub-nosed</ex>
eel</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Snub-nosed cachalot</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>the
pygmy sperm whale.</cd></cs> <-- snub-nosed revolver, a revolver with a
very short barrel. -- -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Snudge</ent>⟦br⟧
